column1: # *** Spelman College Campus Tour (SCCT), Points of Interest (POI) GPS/URL file ***
#This is an ASCII tab-separated-values (TSV) file.  Lines that begin with a '#' are considered to be comments.
#Lines are terminated by a \r.  All fields must be filled out.
#In the case of the URLs, you may enter a *relative* URL, the value NONE or the value USE_DEFAULT.
#NONE indicates that the specified resource is unavailable for the POI.  A value of DEFAULT
#indicates that the resource is at the default URL and has a name of POI_ID.rtf,
#POI_ID.jpg, POI_ID.mp3 or POI_ID.mp4 depending on the resource in question.
#The LATITUDE and LONGITUDE entries are the GPS coordinates of the individual POIs in the file.
#The RADIUS_FT entry is the radius (in feet) around the POI's GPS center where the
#POI is considered to be in range.
#All four resources are not required.  If a video resource is provided, the IMG and AUDIO resources are ignored.
